query:
SELECT om.id, om.user_id, om.org_id, om.role, u.name, u.email, u.platform_owner, o.name as org_name, o.account_id
FROM org_memberships om
JOIN users u ON u.id = om.user_id
JOIN organizations o ON o.id = om.org_id
WHERE u.email LIKE '%junaid%' OR u.name LIKE '%Junaid%'
